  "title": "Logistics Admin (Logistics MNC/ East) - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Receive and verify documents</li>\n  <li>Check customer shipping requirements and transport mode</li>\n  <li>Create sales orders and issue billing in ERP system with proper documents</li>\n  <li>Update records in Excel and share details with operations team</li>\n  <li>Match packing documents with Shipment Management System (SMS)</li>\n  <li>Handle ERP tasks such as purchase requests, receipts, and stock transfers</li>\n  <li>Validate and update weekly/monthly cycle counts in ERP system</li>\n  <li>Communicate with customers via email, Teams, or phone to meet requirements</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with different teams to fulfill customer orders</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc tasks assigned by supervisors/managers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Job Requirements</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma holder</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Office (Word, Excel, Outlook)</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year warehouse experience</li>\n  <li>Able to work accurately in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Comfortable to do OT , including weekends and PH.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270</p>\n<p>Tew Jie Wei | R22106822</p>",
